{"type":"message","id":"b10b26aa","parentId":"ba79b58e","timestamp":"2026-03-01T09:00:28.914Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_044484104dcd47a48fe780a0","toolName":"web_search","content":[{"type":"text","text":"{\n  \"query\": \"ESP32 AI consumer products market analysis 2026 site:medium.com OR site:hackster.io OR site:github.com\",\n  \"provider\": \"brave\",\n  \"count\": 5,\n  \"tookMs\": 1628,\n  \"externalContent\": {\n    \"untrusted\": true,\n    \"source\": \"web_search\",\n    \"provider\": \"brave\",\n    \"wrapped\": true\n  },\n  \"results\": [\n    {\n      \"title\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"f9ada20c04d48360\\\">>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\nOlimex Opens Orders for the \\\"Most Comprehensive and Feature-Rich ESP32-P4 Board on the Market\\\" - Hackster.io\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"f9ada20c04d48360\\\">>>\",\n      \"url\": \"https://www.hackster.io/news/olimex-opens-orders-for-the-most-comprehensive-and-feature-rich-esp32-p4-board-on-the-market-aff3d084d659\",\n      \"description\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"f09ca040595c748d\\\">>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\n&quot;Built around the powerful dual-core [Espressif] ESP32-P4 RISC-V SoC [System-on-Chip], this board delivers serious performance and unmatched peripheral integration for advanced embedded and IoT [Internet of Things] development,&quot; Usunov says of the new Olimex ESP32-P4-PC design. &quot;From HMI [Human-Machine Interface] systems and industrial controllers to edge AI [Artificial Intelligence] and vision applications, the ESP32-P4-PC gives you everything in one board.&quot;\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"f09ca040595c748d\\\">>>\",\n      \"published\": \"4 days ago\",\n      \"siteName\": \"www.hackster.io\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"title\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"47cc7265513b0d74\\\">>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\nAI Detection Industry Report 2026: Market Trends, Accuracy, and Best AI Detect